column6: Marks Scored by the user for each of the questions

column3: =marks for that question if correct; else 0
=sum of scores obtained by the user by question
= sum of marks by question (Maximum that one can get on the test) ref the worksheet TEST CORRECT ANS Data
In a test, there will be multiple themes and for each theme, there may be multiple questions (Refer worksheet - Test Correct Ans data; column BN-CG)
